import React from 'react'
import{ Nav, NavbarContainer, NavLogo} from './NavbarElements';

const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Nav>
        <NavbarContainer>
          <NavLogo to="/">Crafty</NavLogo>
          <MobileIcon>
            <FaBars />
          </MobileIcon>
          <NavMenu>
            <NavItem>
              Nav
            </NavItem>
          </NavMenu>
        </NavbarContainer>
      </Nav>
    </>
  )
}

export default Navbar;
